 "remarks": "Spacious colonial farmhouse with loads of charm, character and wrap-around porch. Lovely open foyer enters into oversized living room with built-ins. Eat-in kitchen with lots of cabinets, oversized windows. Open concept kitchen into dining area. Generous master bedroom with lots of light streaming in. One more nice sized bedroom and/or office and full bath. Washer/dryer in unit. Close to town, restaurants, parks and shopping. 9 minutes to Darien Train Station and 7 minutes to New Canaan Train Station. 10 minutes from the new SoNo Collection Mall. Location, Location, Location! Note: this is a second floor unit",
